<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n16" name="n16">16</a></span>                  <span class="integer">1</span> <span class="integer">0</span> <span class="integer">1</span> <span class="integer">1</span> <span class="integer">0</span> <span class="integer">1</span>    <span class="error">←</span> Corresponds to a <span class="error">‘</span>one<span class="error">’</span> in B
